We, Knoops Limited, are committed to respecting and protecting the privacy of anyone using our site and the confidentiality of any information that you provide us with. This privacy policy explains how we use any personal information we collect about you when you use this website or loyalty app under the law relating to General Data Protection Regulation 2018.
What information do we collect about you?
How will we use the information about you?
